data.description:
Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom brick home, nestled in a prime location just minutes away from shopping, restaurants, and entertainment.  This property offers the perfect blend of convenience and tranquility.

As you step into the inviting entryway, you'll notice neutral paint selections and an open floorplan allowing for seamless flow and abundant natural light throughout.

This property is equipped with a beautifully appointed kitchen featuring tile floors, granite counters, and stainless steel appliances. Additionally, the breakfast bar is perfect for casual dining and entertaining. 

The living areas are adorned with modern fixtures and finishes, providing a sleek and contemporary aesthetic. The tile floors add a touch of sophistication and ensure easy maintenance. 

The master suite boasts a private en-suite bathroom. The additional two bedrooms share a tastefully designed bathroom, with modern fixtures and a clean finish.

Step outside to the private backyard oasis perfect for outdoor relaxation and entertainment under the twinkly lights, sitting fireside.
